[Student "S"]
{Don't bid 2\H. That would be a Reverse, showing at least 17 points. A 2\H bid would also show longer \Cs than \Hs. Don't bid 2\S. That would be showing 4-card support.

So with your minimum hand you bid 1NT which partner raises to 3NT.}

